1¤Rules for using your Visa/Dankort
:SKRSLUT.
.sp 3mm
:SWISS8.
These rules apply to the use of your Visa/Dankort. The rules describe
how to use a Dankort card and a Visa card, as physical card and as the
connected Dankort card on mobile phone, respectively. In
the absence of any statement to the contrary, these rules apply to both
Dankort and Visa cards and as physical card and Dankort card on mobile
phone. The words and expressions used here are explained at the end
of this document.
.sp 5mm
.kp off
.kp on
:SWISS10.
:FED.
2¤What can you use the Visa/Dankort card for?
:SKRSLUT.
.sp 3mm
:SWISS8.
Visa/Dankort is a payment instrument that you can use in Denmark and
abroad.
.sp 3mm
If a store accepts both Dankort and Visa, the store might have
chosen Dankort or Visa as the choice of the store preferred payment
method. You can change the choice of store
where it is technically possible and in accordance with the law.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
:FED.
2.5¤Loyalty programmes
:SKRSLUT.
.br
You can connect Dankort and Visa to different loyalty programmes. Dankort
may only be connected to programmes approved by Nets. You can see
the approved programmes here:
.br
http://dankort.dk/Pages/Loyalitetskort.aspx.
.sp 5mm
.kp off
of goods or services that are unlawful in accordance with
local legislation included.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
When using Visa abroad you may be asked to choose whether the purchase
should be processed in local currency or Danish kroner (see more concerning
this matter in section 18.4).
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
:FED.
2.3¤Withdrawal of sums from your account
:SKRSLUT.
.br
In principle, purchases and cash withdrawals will be debited from your
account on the same day that you make the purchase or withdrawal.
Visa transactions will appear earliest the day after purchase or
withdrawal.
The time of debiting from your account will, however, depend on when
&BANKNAVN. receives the transaction.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
:FED.
2.4¤Maximum consumption
:SKRSLUT.
.br
You may only withdraw cash or make purchases for the balance on your
account, unless you have a different agreement with &BANKNAVN..
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
:KURSIV.
Contactless function or Dankort card on mobile phone
:SKRSLUT.
.br
When using non-contact payment or Dankort card on mobile phone, please
be aware of the maximum limit per transaction without PIN-code
authorisation.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
You will always be able to find the effective maximum amount on
&BANKNAVN.s website. &BANKNAVN. is entitled to change the
amount. Adjustments will not be notified in advance unless the amount
is increased or decreased by more than 50 per cent.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
It will always be evident in your account statement whether a payment
is processed as a Dankort or a Visa transaction.
.sp 3mm
Please observe: fees can be charged when paying with Visa and your monthly
card limit will be written down with the transaction amount (see section
2.4).
.sp 3mm
:FED.
2.1¤Cash withdrawal
:SKRSLUT.
.br
You can use either your Dankort or your Visa to draw money in ATMs that
accepts Dankort or/and Visa. Furthermore you can use your Dankort for cash
withdrawal at the cashier s desk in your own bank and in several other
banks in Denmark and also your Visa in banks that accepts Visa.
.sp 3mm
Please observe: not all ATMs accept Dankort. Thus the cash withdrawal will
be processed as a Visa transaction.
.sp 3mm
Bank fees when using the card and potential limits for use is presented in
&BANKNAVN. s price list.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
:FED.
2.2¤Purchases in shops
:SKRSLUT.
.br
You can use your Visa/Dankort card to pay for goods and services in shops
that accept Dankort and/or Visa.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
You can use your card for purchase on the internet and for mail order and
telephone order purchases. Furthermore you can use
your Visa/Dankort card in automatic machines (e.g. vending machines, ticket
machines).
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
Shops and websites will display whether they accept Dankort and/or Visa.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
Some shops are able to return money to your account, via your
Visa/Dankort card, if you have a positive balance.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
You may not use your Visa/Dankort card for unlawful purposes, purchase
In case the purchase exceeds the effective payment limit, you will
automatically be asked to confirm the payment by entering the PIN
code. At intervals, you may be asked to enter the PIN code, even
though the amount is within the effective payment limit.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
:KURSIV.
Gaming and lottery
:SKRSLUT.
.br
Using your Dankort card with businesses, mainly offering gaming and
betting solutions, including casinos, lottery ticket providers, racing
tracks, etc., a maximum limit for every 24 hours may be specified. The
maximum will appear from the pricelist of the bank in question.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
:KURSIV.
Withdrawal
:SKRSLUT.
.br
A maximum daily withdrawal limit applies to your Dankort card. This sum
is stated on the &BANKNAVN. price list.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
:KURSIV.
Visa card
:SKRSLUT.
.br
Your Visa card has a total limit for purchases and withdrawals for
a rolling 30-day period. Within the total limit, there are separate
limits for how much cash you can withdraw from banks and ATMs per
day. These sums are stated on the bank's price list.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
:KURSIV.
Withdrawal
:SKRSLUT.
.br
In addition, individual businesses can set limits for use of the card.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
Moreover, your bank may have set a limit on the size of the sums you may
withdraw. You may be charged a fee every time you make a cash withdrawal
- irrespective of the sum you withdraw.
.sp 3mm
